{"tid":1296133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"通識科教師賴得鐘FB Post 黑警死全家！ 要辭任考評局委員會主席及通識教師聯會外務副主席","createTime":"2019-07-08T09:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T10:53:09.000Z","uid":28114,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d4127a62d3b7544b5c1594cf64cbbdd4a34bb6e2","tid":1296133,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:19:12.000Z","msg":"【仇警教師】中學通識科教師賴得鐘(右)早前將Facebook (fb) 頭像換成「黑警死全家」，事件引起社會爭議。賴得鐘周日於fb表示，已去信考評局，辭任考評局通識教育科科目委員會主席及成員職務，即時生效，正待考評局正式確認。<br />\n<br />\n賴得鐘亦為香港通識教育教師聯會外務副主席，他亦已去信聯會辭去幹事職務，獲聯會幹事會初步批准。香港通識教育教師聯會於fb表示，收到賴得鐘請辭，將按程序處理。<br />\n<br />\n賴得鐘稱，為免公眾質疑，特此辭去相關職務以正視聽，強調個人言行與所屬組織完全無關。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3152384488135485?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3152384488135485%3Fs%3D753094347%26sfns%3Dmo&d=ng3vG9SJ7BvQZwuOeCzNpZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=9d012d39\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3152384488135485?s=753094347&amp;sfns=mo</a>"},{"pid":"bb719a8684bdd2ade764ce783109480e9c0b2f64","tid":1296133,"uid":126510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:30:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e15fc2fde1677c752e39f965eab553878350b8","tid":1296133,"uid":185960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:30:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d28e9165110b51da4d0dd3a6a054bbcaba8afa4","tid":1296133,"uid":93350,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T09:32:43.000Z","msg":"黑警話要送示威者上死刑台就乜事都冇<br />\n<br />\n老師講句黑警死全家就要辭任<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好大既官威啊</span></span>"},{"pid":"9b3b4aef0a1762b35e742e30b22a67e878b05824","tid":1296133,"uid":213781,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"cit